caption:
Will the limelight make you or break you? Celebrities come and go, but LA County will always be  H O M E.

Famed Status is a semi-plotless celebrity based rpg. This group moves in real time. Relationships and timeline events are up to each player. The only set plot is their home is somewhere within LA County. Everyone is free to travel, leave for work, or the spontaneous road-trip cross country! Come check us out today!

summary: Ok this has been bothering me since the film came out: I did not give a shit about the Enfys Nest reveal so someone please...
body: Ok this has been bothering me since the film came out: I did not give a shit about the Enfys Nest reveal so someone please explain it to me why its such a big deal. Was she a legends character that y'all were waiting to be reinstated in canon? Is she connected to some big character? Or was the reveal that she was a girl supposed to be the big shock? Someone please help me understand.
